  "title": "Class Logger",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Logger'>Class Logger    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Logger.cs#L44'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Static utility methods for backward compatibility with the legacy logging API.\nNOTE: For new code, use LoggerFactory and ILogger directly for better performance\nand flexibility. This class is provided for backward compatibility only.\nUses a default global logger instance.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static class Logger</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger.html'>Logger</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.memberwiseclone'>object.MemberwiseClone()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger._defaultLogger' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger._defaultLogger' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Logger__defaultLogger'>_defaultLogger    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Logger.cs#L49'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The default logger</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private static ILogger _defaultLogger</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogger.html'>ILogger</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger._lock' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger._lock' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Logger__lock'>_lock    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Logger.cs#L54'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The lock</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private static readonly object _lock</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger.Debug(System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Logger.Debug(